1. Decide which business to order from
2. Decide which type of pizza to order
3. Be certain that pizza has pepperoni, mushrooms, black olives and onions
4. Pay for the pizza with some money
5. Wait for pizza to be delivered
6. Enjoy pizza
7. Carefully recycle pizza box and do the dishes
8. Call friends over to have a pizza party
9. Order another pizza

Step 1a. If there is no pizza delivery service, quickly pack up your bags and move.
     1b. Once in new location, return to step 1.